# pip-audit vulnerability ignore list
#
# Each non-blank, non-comment line is a vulnerability ID (CVE/PYSEC/GHSA)
# passed to pip-audit via --ignore-vuln during CI.
#
# The update-project.sh script automatically sweeps this file after dependency
# upgrades: it re-tests each entry, removes any that are now fixed, and reports
# which remain. Only add entries here when no fix is available upstream.
#
# Format: VULN-ID  # package==version — short description (date added)
